Girls who have just arrived in cities for higher education must know there are sexual predators who’ll target them. These men will tempt them with gifts, only to sleep with them. Young women must never forget they are there to acquire education to become self-reliant. They should be guided by their goals and never allow anyone or anything to mislead them. Sugar daddies are notorious for promising girls heaven and earth. Girls, don’t be tempted by the riches a man may have or the car he drives. Channelling your energy into your ultimate goal is the way to create your own wealth. ) One of the best tricks to survive your first year at varsity is to befriend someone senior to you. You can also check who from your kasi is attending that university and stay close to them. This way, they are able to help you navigate this jungle. The matter you are raising here can either make or break someone.     There are usually no second chances at varsity, so you need to nail it the first time around. All young women embarking on this journey must be aware of the risks out there. This letter wins our R200 daily prize. Call Nthabiseng at our office to collect.   X   Deputy Editor